  <h1>DevUtil</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
    Privacy-first collection of developer utilities running locally in browser
  </p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    A comprehensive, privacy-first collection of developer utilities for everyday tasks—all running locally 
    in your browser. Perfect for quick conversions, encoding/decoding, code formatting, testing, and more.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>100% client-side processing - All tools run in your browser</li>
    <li>Zero server calls - Your data never leaves your device</li>
    <li>No tracking - No analytics, cookies, or data collection</li>
    <li>Open source - Full transparency, inspect the code yourself</li>
    <li>Offline capable - Works without internet after initial load</li>
    <li>Multiple utility categories - Encoding, formatting, testing, conversions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tool Categories</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Encoders/Decoders</li>
    <li>Code formatters</li>
    <li>Converters</li>
    <li>Generators</li>
    <li>Testing utilities</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Status</h2>
